to take the heart out of heart.

00:01:59.486 --> 00:02:01.255 align:middle line:84%
We're not trying to make
it sterile or mental,

00:02:01.255 --> 00:02:03.357 align:middle line:84%
but we knew it needed
a connection.

00:02:03.357 --> 00:02:04.558 align:middle line:84%
So, what our scientists
have done

00:02:04.558 --> 00:02:07.094 align:middle line:84%
over these years is really
tell an amazing story,

00:02:07.094 --> 00:02:08.361 align:middle line:84%
starting with the
physical heart,

00:02:08.361 --> 00:02:10.397 align:middle line:84%
about how it's more
than a blood pump.

00:02:10.397 --> 00:02:13.567 align:middle line:84%
It's really an information
processing center in our bodies,

00:02:13.567 --> 00:02:15.703 align:middle line:84%
communicating powerful
messages to the brain

00:02:15.703 --> 00:02:17.972 align:middle line:84%
and throughout the entire
system, and they've mapped

00:02:17.972 --> 00:02:20.241 align:middle line:84%
out how it does all that, and
they've shown very clearly

00:02:20.241 --> 00:02:22.743 align:middle line:84%
through published peer
reviewed scientific resource

00:02:22.743 --> 00:02:25.812 align:middle line:84%
that it does do a lot
more than pump blood.

00:02:25.812 --> 00:02:28.549 align:middle line:84%
Beyond that, we all know
about the spiritual heart.

00:02:28.549 --> 00:02:33.654 align:middle line:84%
And, to me, it's that
part of us where spirit;

00:02:33.654 --> 00:02:35.788 align:middle line:84%
something that's larger than
