00:02:42.730 --> 00:02:44.698 align:middle line:84%
that sometimes we
think we can't.

00:02:44.698 --> 00:02:46.967 align:middle line:84%
It's the source of
our self-security.

00:02:46.967 --> 00:02:48.401 align:middle line:90%
It's the source of our wisdom.

00:02:48.401 --> 00:02:49.236 align:middle line:90%
It's high speed.

00:02:49.236 --> 00:02:50.638 align:middle line:90%
It's intuitive.

00:02:50.638 --> 00:02:53.173 align:middle line:84%
It gives us new clarity and new
understanding about ourselves,

00:02:53.173 --> 00:02:55.409 align:middle line:84%
about each other,
and about life.

00:02:55.409 --> 00:02:56.410 align:middle line:84%
And, one of the thing
that I've learned

00:02:56.410 --> 00:02:57.745 align:middle line:90%
about heart all these years,

00:02:57.745 --> 00:03:00.547 align:middle line:84%
is that it's really
my own best friend,

00:03:00.547 --> 00:03:04.285 align:middle line:84%
and my most reliable guide that
I have to making the decisions,

00:03:04.285 --> 00:03:08.589 align:middle line:84%
big ones or small ones, that I
need to make as I navigate life.

