which removes the barriers

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:55.976 align:middle line:84%
and time and space that
Newtonian physics has.

00:07:55.976 --> 00:07:58.412 align:middle line:84%
Then this field becomes
very, very large,

00:07:58.412 --> 00:07:59.746 align:middle line:90%
maybe even infinite in a way.

00:07:59.746 --> 00:08:02.649 align:middle line:84%
It could be influencing and
connecting with things far,

00:08:02.649 --> 00:08:05.452 align:middle line:84%
far beyond our time and
space understanding.

00:08:05.452 --> 00:08:07.821 align:middle line:84%
So, it's my belief that
we, that through all

00:08:07.821 --> 00:08:10.457 align:middle line:84%
of this communication,
biological, electromagnetic,

00:08:10.457 --> 00:08:12.960 align:middle line:84%
all the other energetic fields
that are probably associated

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:16.463 align:middle line:84%
with heart, that's where we are
actually accessing the field

00:08:16.463 --> 00:08:17.798 align:middle line:90%
of the consciousness.

00:08:17.798 --> 00:08:21.034 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness meaning that
infinite field of information

00:08:21.034 --> 00:08:23.170 align:middle line:84%
that we draw from
to create reality,

00:08:23.170 --> 00:08:24.838 align:middle line:84%
whatever reality
happens to be for us

00:08:24.838 --> 00:08:26.406 align:middle line:90%
through our human filters.

00:08:26.406 --> 00:08:28.842 align:middle line:84%
And, it's through heart where
we make that connection.

00:08:28.842 --> 00:08:31.811 align:middle line:84%
It's transmitted at
super-high speed to the brain.

00:08:31.811 --> 00:08:34.348 align:middle line:84%
The brain has this amazing
information processing center

00:08:34.348 --> 00:08:36.416 align:middle line:84%
that we have that
interprets and compares,

00:08:36.416 --> 00:08:39.186 align:middle line:84%
and compartmentalizes
things, and so it looks

00:08:39.186 --> 00:08:40.287 align:middle line:90%
like the brain is doing it all.

00:08:40.287 --> 00:08:42.421 align:middle line:84%
But, my belief is
they work together,

00:08:42.421 --> 00:08:43.624 align:middle line:90%
and that the information

00:08:43.624 --> 00:08:46.059 align:middle line:84%
from consciousness enters
the biological system

00:08:46.059 --> 00:08:47.361 align:middle line:90%
at the level of heart.

00:08:47.361 --> 00:08:48.829 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: I have a
question regarding that,

00:08:48.829 --> 00:08:51.832 align:middle line:84%
because I had the honor to
interview Pim van Lommel,

00:08:51.832 --> 00:08:55.469 align:middle line:84%
you know, the cardiologue
that is based in New Zealand

00:08:55.469 --> 00:08:59.039 align:middle line:84%
that who have studies and
had many, many heart arrests

00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:03.143 align:middle line:84%
in front of him, and yet
those people were able

00:09:03.143 --> 00:09:06.613 align:middle line:84%
to experience an NDE, so
how do you explain that?

00:09:06.613 --> 00:09:08.015 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: What's an NDE?

00:09:08.015 --> 00:09:09.883 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: No, how do you
explain the fact, yeah,

00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:11.218 align:middle line:90%
near death experience.

00:09:11.218 --> 00:09:14.888 align:middle line:84%
Because most of the people
would say, you know, oh, well,

00:09:14.888 --> 00:09:16.223 align:middle line:90%
you can't have an NDE.

00:09:16.223 --> 00:09:19.226 align:middle line:84%
You know, there's the heart,
is it created by the brain,

00:09:19.226 --> 00:09:22.429 align:middle line:84%
but here you're saying
consciousness is accessed

00:09:22.429 --> 00:09:23.563 align:middle line:90%
through the heart, right?

00:09:23.563 --> 00:09:26.400 align:middle line:84%
So, I'm wondering how
that works with NDE's.

00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:27.834 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: I don't
know, it's hard to say.

00:09:27.834 --> 00:09:29.336 align:middle line:84%
It's a question I've
never been asked before.

00:09:29.336 --> 00:09:32.039 align:middle line:84%
I mean that what I was saying
earlier is that, you know,

00:09:32.039 --> 00:09:34.541 align:middle line:84%
consciousness enters our
system in a variety of ways.

00:09:34.541 --> 00:09:37.944 align:middle line:84%
I think what the heart is
is really a bioreceptor

00:09:37.944 --> 00:09:41.148 align:middle line:84%
of intuitive information,
and that's what's happening.

00:09:41.148 --> 00:09:43.817 align:middle line:84%
So, in a near-death experience,
when people leave the body,

00:09:43.817 --> 00:09:46.186 align:middle line:84%
they go someplace else, they
experience something different.

00:09:46.186 --> 00:09:48.188 align:middle line:84%
You know, time becomes
very different.

00:09:48.188 --> 00:09:49.956 align:middle line:84%
They can feel like they
were there a long time,

00:09:49.956 --> 00:09:51.258 align:middle line:84%
and it's been a matter
of minutes

00:09:51.258 --> 00:09:55.162 align:middle line:84%
that they were pronounced
dead, etc. It's just hard

00:09:55.162 --> 00:09:57.998 align:middle line:84%
to say how the heart and
brain, either one play

00:09:57.998 --> 00:09:59.332 align:middle line:90%
into that particular situation.

00:09:59.332 --> 00:10:02.502 align:middle line:84%
I haven't ever studied that,
and I've talked to people

00:10:02.502 --> 00:10:03.770 align:middle line:90%
who have had that experience.

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:05.772 align:middle line:84%
So, I know that they've
been very real with me

00:10:05.772 --> 00:10:07.274 align:middle line:84%
about what they've
said about it.

00:10:07.274 --> 00:10:08.842 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: They had that
unconditional love,

00:10:08.842 --> 00:10:10.110 align:middle line:90%
and they felt all those.

00:10:10.110 --> 00:10:11.011 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: And they really
didn't want to come back.

00:10:11.011 --> 00:10:12.446 align:middle line:90%
It was a service to come back.

00:10:12.446 --> 00:10:15.115 align:middle line:84%
It was like, we fear death,
and the ones that I've talked

00:10:15.115 --> 00:10:16.483 align:middle line:84%
to have said, you
know, you're there,

00:10:16.483 --> 00:10:21.088 align:middle line:84%
and it's really a choice you
make to come back, because it's

00:10:21.088 --> 00:10:26.326 align:middle line:84%
so freeing and so magnificent,
that it's beyond the density

00:10:26.326 --> 00:10:28.328 align:middle line:84%
that we experience
here on earth.

00:10:28.328 --> 00:10:30.997 align:middle line:84%
So, they have to make choices
about even wanting to come back,

00:10:30.997 --> 00:10:32.432 align:middle line:84%
and it's usually a
choice of service,

00:10:32.432 --> 00:10:34.334 align:middle line:84%
that they recognize
there's more work to do

00:10:34.334 --> 00:10:37.304 align:middle line:84%
in assisting this
world and humanity

00:10:37.304 --> 00:10:39.172 align:middle line:90%
through a transitional time.

00:10:39.172 --> 00:10:40.907 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: So, sorry I
stopped in your explanation,

00:10:40.907 --> 00:10:44.244 align:middle line:84%
but I got really excited,
because you said this is a way

00:10:44.244 --> 00:10:46.413 align:middle line:84%
for us to access
other dimensions,

00:10:46.413 --> 00:10:47.981 align:middle line:90%
even our actually consciousness.

00:10:47.981 --> 00:10:48.982 align:middle line:90%
>> That's exactly right.

00:10:48.982 --> 00:10:50.283 align:middle line:84%
I think that's what's
happening anyway

00:10:50.283 --> 00:10:53.186 align:middle line:84%
and the more loving we are
and the more caring we are,

00:10:53.186 --> 00:10:55.288 align:middle line:84%
these things, the
more receptive we are.

00:10:55.288 --> 00:10:57.491 align:middle line:90%
The more this field is coherent,

00:10:57.491 --> 00:10:59.126 align:middle line:84%
and a coherent field
will receive more

00:10:59.126 --> 00:11:00.394 align:middle line:90%
of that information.

00:11:00.394 --> 00:11:02.195 align:middle line:84%
So, it goes right back to
some basic stuff in life

00:11:02.195 --> 00:11:04.731 align:middle line:84%
that we all know that we
just need to practice more.

00:11:04.731 --> 00:11:07.734 align:middle line:84%
We need to appreciate all the
things we have in our life.

00:11:07.734 --> 00:11:09.536 align:middle line:84%
We need to be more
caring towards other.

00:11:09.536 --> 00:11:12.372 align:middle line:84%
We need to be more compassionate
and less judgmental.

00:11:12.372 --> 00:11:13.607 align:middle line:90%
We need to have more love.

00:11:13.607 --> 00:11:15.442 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I believe the
purpose of life is to love.

00:11:15.442 --> 00:11:16.676 align:middle line:90%
I know that sounds simplistic.

00:11:16.676 --> 00:11:18.011 align:middle line:90%
I know it sounds philosophical.

00:11:18.011 --> 00:11:19.279 align:middle line:90%
Hey, life's tough out there.

00:11:19.279 --> 00:11:22.149 align:middle line:84%
You don't understand all
that, but the more I do this,

00:11:22.149 --> 00:11:24.618 align:middle line:84%
and the older that I get, the
more I recognize that I believe

00:11:24.618 --> 00:11:25.886 align:middle line:90%
that that's the purpose.

00:11:25.886 --> 00:11:27.087 align:middle line:90%
Is to love.

00:11:27.087 --> 00:11:29.923 align:middle line:84%
It's the universal, you
know, source of creation.

00:11:29.923 --> 00:11:31.892 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Fabric
of the universe.

00:11:31.892 --> 00:11:33.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Fabric of the
universe, and our ability

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.662 align:middle line:84%
to put more of that out, and
to push past the barriers

00:11:35.662 --> 00:11:37.364 align:middle line:84%
and thresholds where
we stop doing it,

00:11:37.364 --> 00:11:40.233 align:middle line:84%
where we have the resistances
and the judgments and things.

00:11:40.233 --> 00:11:41.568 align:middle line:90%
That's the real work.

00:11:41.568 --> 00:11:43.603 align:middle line:84%
The more we do of that, and
that's a heart kind of work

00:11:43.603 --> 00:11:47.773 align:middle line:84%
in my opinion, the more we begin
to then receive new information

00:11:47.773 --> 00:11:50.010 align:middle line:90%
that allows us to be more aware,

00:11:50.010 --> 00:11:51.545 align:middle line:84%
more conscious, more
intelligent.

00:11:51.545 --> 00:11:54.447 align:middle line:84%
So, to me, it comes back
to the manifestation

00:11:54.447 --> 00:11:56.583 align:middle line:84%
of these heart qualities
in a practical way,

00:11:56.583 --> 00:11:59.419 align:middle line:84%
taken out of sentimental
associations,

00:11:59.419 --> 00:12:01.988 align:middle line:84%
applied in our daily lives,
and how we make choices

00:12:01.988 --> 00:12:04.591 align:middle line:84%
and how we interact with
others is really how we come

00:12:04.591 --> 00:12:08.161 align:middle line:84%
into the new intelligence,
that we are coming into anyway,

00:12:08.161 --> 00:12:12.365 align:middle line:84%
but that we need to begin the
solve the personal, societal,

00:12:12.365 --> 00:12:14.267 align:middle line:84%
and global problems
we have today.

00:12:14.267 --> 00:12:18.572 align:middle line:84%
It still comes to accessing
more of the frequency of love.

00:12:18.572 --> 00:12:22.542 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: And this is something
you think our whole society can

00:12:22.542 --> 00:12:24.211 align:middle line:90%
be a heart-based society?

00:12:24.211 --> 00:12:25.512 align:middle line:90%
Can we get there?

00:12:25.512 --> 00:12:26.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Yeah,
that's what we do here.

00:12:26.980 --> 00:12:28.448 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we're trying to, you
asked the question earlier,

00:12:28.448 --> 00:12:29.916 align:middle line:90%
what do we do here at HeartMath?

00:12:29.916 --> 00:12:32.519 align:middle line:84%
Well, we're really trying to
create a more heart-based world,

00:12:32.519 --> 00:12:34.120 align:middle line:84%
and we do that again
in a variety

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:36.022 align:middle line:90%
of different ways to do that.

00:12:36.022 --> 00:12:38.525 align:middle line:84%
And, yes, I think that
part of this era that we're

00:12:38.525 --> 00:12:40.627 align:middle line:84%
in now that's been
generically called the shift.

00:12:40.627 --> 00:12:42.429 align:middle line:90%
An important part of that is

00:12:42.429 --> 00:12:44.698 align:middle line:84%
that heart-directed
living is part

00:12:44.698 --> 00:12:46.766 align:middle line:90%
of the evolutionary imperative.

00:12:46.766 --> 00:12:48.401 align:middle line:84%
That's not HeartMath
by any means.

00:12:48.401 --> 00:12:49.870 align:middle line:90%
It's way bigger than HeartMath.

00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:52.439 align:middle line:84%
We've just been pretty good
at putting language around,

00:12:52.439 --> 00:12:54.307 align:middle line:84%
some simple tools,
some simple techniques,

00:12:54.307 --> 00:12:56.610 align:middle line:84%
some things that people can
then apply in their life

00:12:56.610 --> 00:12:58.245 align:middle line:84%
to create this heart-based
world,

00:12:58.245 --> 00:13:00.380 align:middle line:90%
but it's much bigger than that.

00:13:00.380 --> 00:13:02.649 align:middle line:90%
We call it heart intelligence,

00:13:02.649 --> 00:13:06.386 align:middle line:84%
a high-speed intuitive
intelligence that manifests

00:13:06.386 --> 00:13:08.088 align:middle line:90%
from our authentic self.

00:13:08.088 --> 00:13:10.156 align:middle line:90%
And, as we have more of that,

00:13:10.156 --> 00:13:11.892 align:middle line:84%
I think we are moving
that way anyway.

00:13:11.892 --> 00:13:14.494 align:middle line:84%
I feel like things are in a
good place within the context

00:13:14.494 --> 00:13:16.496 align:middle line:90%
of the evolutionary shift.

00:13:16.496 --> 00:13:17.898 align:middle line:90%
It is a dimensional shift.

00:13:17.898 --> 00:13:20.700 align:middle line:84%
It's a change in the
consciousness fabric itself.

00:13:20.700 --> 00:13:25.272 align:middle line:84%
Our mutual friend, Barbara Marx
Hubbard, calls it a memetic,

00:13:25.272 --> 00:13:27.741 align:middle line:90%
change in the memetic code.

00:13:27.741 --> 00:13:32.078 align:middle line:84%
A meme is a mass thought
form, so to speak,

00:13:32.078 --> 00:13:34.481 align:middle line:84%
that we don't even question,
you know, it's so big.

00:13:34.481 --> 00:13:37.250 align:middle line:84%
We don't even see it, it's
so big, like big is better,

00:13:37.250 --> 00:13:38.485 align:middle line:90%
you know, those kinds of things.

00:13:38.485 --> 00:13:39.619 align:middle line:90%
They're just sort of build

00:13:39.619 --> 00:13:41.288 align:middle line:84%
into the psychological
framework that we have.

00:13:41.288 --> 00:13:42.222 align:middle line:90%
We don't even challenge them.

00:13:42.222 --> 00:13:43.623 align:middle line:90%
They're just there.

00:13:43.623 --> 00:13:48.161 align:middle line:84%
But, what she says is just like
the genetic code is changing,

00:13:48.161 --> 00:13:51.131 align:middle line:84%
that the memetic code of
consciousness is changing.

00:13:51.131 --> 00:13:52.465 align:middle line:84%
I believe she's right
about that.

00:13:52.465 --> 00:13:55.235 align:middle line:84%
I think what we are involving
now is a dimensional shift

00:13:55.235 --> 00:13:56.870 align:middle line:90%
in consciousness.

00:13:56.870 --> 00:14:00.206 align:middle line:84%
It's the biggest shift that
there's been since there's been,

00:14:00.206 --> 00:14:02.008 align:middle line:84%
you know, human beings
on the planet.

00:14:02.008 --> 00:14:04.844 align:middle line:84%
We're moving from a baseline of
third dimensional consciousness,

00:14:04.844 --> 00:14:09.382 align:middle line:84%
which is, I mean, it's
okay, it's separate,

00:14:09.382 --> 00:14:10.951 align:middle line:90%
it's good, bad, right and wrong.

00:14:10.951 --> 00:14:12.085 align:middle line:90%
It's ambition.

00:14:12.085 --> 00:14:12.886 align:middle line:90%
It's survival.

00:14:12.886 --> 00:14:14.120 align:middle line:90%
It's those kinds of things,

00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:15.522 align:middle line:84%
but look at the beauty
that it's built.

00:14:15.522 --> 00:14:18.224 align:middle line:84%
So, it's not to say
that it's all bad.

00:14:18.224 --> 00:14:19.993 align:middle line:84%
But, we're moving now
into the fourth dimension,

00:14:19.993 --> 00:14:21.394 align:middle line:84%
and where we're trying
to get to,

00:14:21.394 --> 00:14:24.531 align:middle line:84%
and we are getting there very
quickly is to the higher ranges

00:14:24.531 --> 00:14:25.865 align:middle line:90%
of the fourth dimension.

00:14:25.865 --> 00:14:28.068 align:middle line:84%
So, what's happening is we're
really making a dimension

00:14:28.068 --> 00:14:31.905 align:middle line:84%
and a half shift over a
very short period of time.

00:14:31.905 --> 00:14:34.541 align:middle line:84%
I estimate, you know,
about a hundred years,

00:14:34.541 --> 00:14:36.710 align:middle line:84%
that we're in the
middle of it right now.

00:14:36.710 --> 00:14:39.279 align:middle line:84%
About a hundred year
little window of time,

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:41.381 align:middle line:84%
we're making this huge
dimensional shift.

00:14:41.381 --> 00:14:43.616 align:middle line:90%
Well, that much change happening

00:14:43.616 --> 00:14:46.753 align:middle line:84%
so quickly creates a
huge amount of chaos.

00:14:46.753 --> 00:14:47.487 align:middle line:90%
We see that.

00:14:47.487 --> 00:14:48.288 align:middle line:90%
We see the wars.

00:14:48.288 --> 00:14:49.556 align:middle line:90%
We see the social inequity.

00:14:49.556 --> 00:14:51.091 align:middle line:90%
We see the economic issues.

00:14:51.091 --> 00:14:54.160 align:middle line:84%
We see all those things, and
they're displayed so prominently

00:14:54.160 --> 00:14:58.565 align:middle line:84%
to us, and all we have to do
is look at a news site or turn

00:14:58.565 --> 00:15:00.500 align:middle line:84%
on the TV, and it's like,
I can't believe this.

00:15:00.500 --> 00:15:03.036 align:middle line:84%
You know, we see those
pictures so vividly.

00:15:03.036 --> 00:15:06.806 align:middle line:84%
What I think we want to also
recognize is all the other

00:15:06.806 --> 00:15:09.309 align:middle line:84%
changes that are happening
that are all the other changes

00:15:09.309 --> 00:15:11.578 align:middle line:84%
that are happening that are
really positive and really good,

00:15:11.578 --> 00:15:13.279 align:middle line:84%
and that they are happening
very quickly as well.

00:15:13.279 --> 00:15:15.248 align:middle line:84%
Millions and millions
and millions of people,

00:15:15.248 --> 00:15:16.716 align:middle line:84%
and you know this
just as well as I do,

00:15:16.716 --> 00:15:19.853 align:middle line:84%
all around the world are
operating in new states

00:15:19.853 --> 00:15:21.588 align:middle line:90%
of awareness and consciousness.

00:15:21.588 --> 00:15:23.590 align:middle line:84%
They've developed new
values, new interest,

00:15:23.590 --> 00:15:26.826 align:middle line:84%
new ways of living, new
levels of cooperation,

00:15:26.826 --> 00:15:28.294 align:middle line:90%
new levels of making an effort

00:15:28.294 --> 00:15:30.397 align:middle line:84%
to not separate,
but rather unite.

00:15:30.397 --> 00:15:33.299 align:middle line:84%
All those things are
happening all over the planet,

00:15:33.299 --> 00:15:36.269 align:middle line:84%
so we are moving to a
more heart-based world.

00:15:36.269 --> 00:15:37.604 align:middle line:84%
So, yeah, people
are going to get it.

00:15:37.604 --> 00:15:39.506 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't mean everybody will.

00:15:39.506 --> 00:15:41.508 align:middle line:84%
You've got to be practical
about these things.

00:15:41.508 --> 00:15:43.276 align:middle line:84%
There are people who will
never believe in this.

00:15:43.276 --> 00:15:46.546 align:middle line:84%
People that don't
want to live that way.

00:15:46.546 --> 00:15:48.848 align:middle line:90%
It's not how they see the world.

00:15:48.848 --> 00:15:50.216 align:middle line:90%
It's not their world view.

00:15:50.216 --> 00:15:52.252 align:middle line:84%
At the same time, there
are millions and millions

00:15:52.252 --> 00:15:53.820 align:middle line:84%
and millions, like I've
said around the world

00:15:53.820 --> 00:15:55.422 align:middle line:90%
who are seeing that way.

00:15:55.422 --> 00:15:57.824 align:middle line:84%
Not that they're calling
it heart-based world,

00:15:57.824 --> 00:16:00.527 align:middle line:84%
but they're manifesting
the qualities of heart.

00:16:00.527 --> 00:16:03.363 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Should could there
be actually two different

00:16:03.363 --> 00:16:06.232 align:middle line:84%
societies, or like a new
earth on the same earth,

00:16:06.232 --> 00:16:08.501 align:middle line:84%
and two different kind of
current, one based on fear,

00:16:08.501 --> 00:16:09.502 align:middle line:90%
the other one on love?

00:16:09.502 --> 00:16:10.437 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: I think
it already exists.

00:16:10.437 --> 00:16:11.471 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:16:11.471 --> 00:16:14.374 align:middle line:84%
That seems deeper
the bigger it gets.

00:16:14.374 --> 00:16:17.143 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: The polarization
is becoming more obvious.

00:16:17.143 --> 00:16:18.978 align:middle line:84%
You know, what I see,
just a visual image of it,

00:16:18.978 --> 00:16:21.014 align:middle line:84%
I see a new world birthing
itself in the middle

00:16:21.014 --> 00:16:24.150 align:middle line:84%
of the old one, and it's push
out like this as it grows.

00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:25.185 align:middle line:84%
And, the old one
is pushing back,

00:16:25.185 --> 00:16:26.820 align:middle line:84%
because it doesn't
want to go away.

00:16:26.820 --> 00:16:29.055 align:middle line:84%
Where the two meet,
there's friction,

00:16:29.055 --> 00:16:31.491 align:middle line:84%
and that friction is
what we see on the news,

00:16:31.491 --> 00:16:33.960 align:middle line:84%
but the new one is emerging,
and it can't be stopped.

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:36.062 align:middle line:84%
It's like, this shift
is bigger than us.

00:16:36.062 --> 00:16:37.197 align:middle line:90%
It's bigger than humanity.

00:16:37.197 --> 00:16:38.431 align:middle line:90%
It's bigger than planet earth.

00:16:38.431 --> 00:16:40.667 align:middle line:84%
It's a big, big shift that's
happening throughout the

00:16:40.667 --> 00:16:42.168 align:middle line:90%
cosmos really.

00:16:42.168 --> 00:16:44.104 align:middle line:90%
So, it's a matter not of if.

00:16:44.104 --> 00:16:47.173 align:middle line:84%
It's a matter of how easy
or how hard do we make it.

00:16:47.173 --> 00:16:50.343 align:middle line:84%
So, part of what we do here
at HeartMath is provide people

00:16:50.343 --> 00:16:52.479 align:middle line:84%
with the skills they
need to make it a kinder,

00:16:52.479 --> 00:16:54.681 align:middle line:90%
gentler process, and then

00:16:54.681 --> 00:16:57.817 align:middle line:84%
to help others make it a
kinder, gentler process.

00:16:57.817 --> 00:16:59.252 align:middle line:84%
Because it's going
to happen anyway.

00:16:59.252 --> 00:17:00.420 align:middle line:90%
It's already happening.

00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:02.288 align:middle line:84%
It's just a matter of
how rough it's going

00:17:02.288 --> 00:17:03.690 align:middle line:90%
to be to get it there.

00:17:03.690 --> 00:17:04.724 align:middle line:90%
But, there are two worlds

00:17:04.724 --> 00:17:06.259 align:middle line:84%
in a sense operating
in the same place.

00:17:06.259 --> 00:17:07.627 align:middle line:90%
I've wondered about that.

00:17:07.627 --> 00:17:12.698 align:middle line:84%
When I think about something
like how society operates here

00:17:12.698 --> 00:17:16.336 align:middle line:84%
in the western world, and
my values or all the people

00:17:16.336 --> 00:17:18.037 align:middle line:84%
that I'm associated
with on base,

00:17:18.037 --> 00:17:24.344 align:middle line:84%
and I how people could
have a genocidal war,

00:17:24.344 --> 00:17:26.079 align:middle line:90%
let's say in Subsahara Africa,

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:28.181 align:middle line:84%
and the horrific
things that go on there.

00:17:28.181 --> 00:17:31.484 align:middle line:90%
Is that the same planet I'm on?

00:17:31.484 --> 00:17:33.686 align:middle line:84%
And, I'm not saying
that from a judgment

00:17:33.686 --> 00:17:34.788 align:middle line:90%
of those people or anything.

00:17:34.788 --> 00:17:36.189 align:middle line:84%
It's just like it's
two different worlds.

00:17:36.189 --> 00:17:38.191 align:middle line:84%
I mean to be able
to do those things

00:17:38.191 --> 00:17:42.228 align:middle line:84%
to each other is beyond
anything comprehensible in me

00:17:42.228 --> 00:17:44.030 align:middle line:90%
or anything around me.

00:17:44.030 --> 00:17:46.699 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: And it's not the
heart doesn't see it, right?

00:17:46.699 --> 00:17:48.535 align:middle line:90%
When you have this heart-based,

00:17:48.535 --> 00:17:50.904 align:middle line:84%
heart intelligence,
you see that reality.

00:17:50.904 --> 00:17:53.807 align:middle line:84%
You see the suffering,
but how do you.

00:17:53.807 --> 00:17:57.110 align:middle line:84%
But, it seems like it gives
actually even more strength.

00:17:57.110 --> 00:17:59.646 align:middle line:84%
The heart actually
seems to [noise].

00:17:59.646 --> 00:18:01.614 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Yeah, well, you
