00:18:01.614 --> 00:18:03.650 align:middle line:84%
and higher aspect of heart,
and the lower aspect is

00:18:03.650 --> 00:18:07.220 align:middle line:84%
like the different between let's
say compassion and sympathy.

00:18:07.220 --> 00:18:08.321 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:18:08.321 --> 00:18:10.356 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Sympathy
is oh the poor people,

00:18:10.356 --> 00:18:12.659 align:middle line:84%
and it sort of has this
draggy energy to it.

00:18:12.659 --> 00:18:16.162 align:middle line:84%
It feels like it's bringing
your down, with all this worry

00:18:16.162 --> 00:18:17.664 align:middle line:90%
and concern and everything.

00:18:17.664 --> 00:18:19.165 align:middle line:84%
Compassion would
be a higher place

00:18:19.165 --> 00:18:21.568 align:middle line:84%
of really having
an understanding

00:18:21.568 --> 00:18:23.303 align:middle line:84%
of what these people are
going through; feeling it,

00:18:23.303 --> 00:18:25.305 align:middle line:90%
but not being immersed in it.

00:18:25.305 --> 00:18:27.974 align:middle line:84%
And, in that higher
compassion, the energetic output

00:18:27.974 --> 00:18:29.876 align:middle line:90%
of service is much more potent.

00:18:29.876 --> 00:18:32.111 align:middle line:84%
Sympathy has got a draggy
kind of energy to it.

00:18:32.111 --> 00:18:35.014 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't have the same
level of effectiveness

00:18:35.014 --> 00:18:36.616 align:middle line:90%
that real compassion does.

00:18:36.616 --> 00:18:38.418 align:middle line:84%
So, the deeper we
are in our own heart,

00:18:38.418 --> 00:18:41.120 align:middle line:84%
the more we make connection
with that heart intelligence

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:44.357 align:middle line:84%
in ourselves, the more
self-secure we are

00:18:44.357 --> 00:18:48.494 align:middle line:84%
to be able make choices about
how compassionate we should be

00:18:48.494 --> 00:18:51.164 align:middle line:84%
about something,
versus how sympathetic.

00:18:51.164 --> 00:18:55.401 align:middle line:84%
Those discriminations are
part of an intelligence

00:18:55.401 --> 00:18:58.204 align:middle line:84%
that gives us the ability to see
more into ourselves and to see

00:18:58.204 --> 00:18:59.472 align:middle line:90%
into each other, and that's one

00:18:59.472 --> 00:19:00.807 align:middle line:84%
of the beautiful
things about heart.

00:19:00.807 --> 00:19:03.076 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Um hum, um hum,
