to see the commonality.

00:19:14.787 --> 00:19:16.389 align:middle line:84%
An example that gets
talked about a lot

00:19:16.389 --> 00:19:19.626 align:middle line:84%
in various circles is
we're moving from an era

00:19:19.626 --> 00:19:22.195 align:middle line:84%
