era of cooperation.

00:19:22.195 --> 00:19:25.231 align:middle line:84%
Right? That's said a lot in the
business circles and things, so,

00:19:25.231 --> 00:19:27.500 align:middle line:84%
what that means is we're
trying to be less separate.

00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:29.769 align:middle line:84%
We're trying to be more
accepting of each other.

00:19:29.769 --> 00:19:32.705 align:middle line:84%
Allowing for the uniqueness,
not trying to take that away

00:19:32.705 --> 00:19:34.841 align:middle line:84%
from someone or make
them like you.

00:19:34.841 --> 00:19:37.110 align:middle line:84%
It's more like, maybe
I'm not like them.

00:19:37.110 --> 00:19:39.679 align:middle line:84%
Maybe I don't even agree with
them totally, but I can sort

00:19:39.679 --> 00:19:44.350 align:middle line:84%
of appreciate what they are,
maybe how they got there.

00:19:44.350 --> 00:19:46.519 align:middle line:84%
Another thing I see breaking
down, this will relate to you

