fair, you know,

00:22:22.809 --> 00:22:25.011 align:middle line:84%
something that I
don't think was right?

00:22:25.011 --> 00:22:26.813 align:middle line:90%
What's my attitude going to be?

00:22:26.813 --> 00:22:28.881 align:middle line:90%
Is that where love stops?

00:22:28.881 --> 00:22:33.286 align:middle line:84%
Or is there a pause where
I maintain a certain poise,

00:22:33.286 --> 00:22:35.021 align:middle line:90%
a certain ability.

00:22:35.021 --> 00:22:37.990 align:middle line:84%
Now necessarily agree
with it, but deal with it

00:22:37.990 --> 00:22:42.061 align:middle line:84%
from a little different place
