00:23:13.726 --> 00:23:15.428 align:middle line:84%
The things we teach in
our training problems.

00:23:15.428 --> 00:23:17.930 align:middle line:84%
The things we teach like in
our heart mastery courses

00:23:17.930 --> 00:23:19.098 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:23:19.098 --> 00:23:21.267 align:middle line:84%
There are techniques
that we developed

00:23:21.267 --> 00:23:23.169 align:middle line:84%
that were intentionally
designed to be simple.

00:23:23.169 --> 00:23:26.873 align:middle line:84%
We had to work to make them
simple, and the reason wanted

00:23:26.873 --> 00:23:28.441 align:middle line:84%
to make them simple
is we recognize

00:23:28.441 --> 00:23:30.776 align:middle line:84%
in the fast-paced
worlds of these times,

00:23:30.776 --> 00:23:32.178 align:middle line:84%
people are not going
to spend a lot

00:23:32.178 --> 00:23:34.280 align:middle line:90%
of time trying to get somewhere.

00:23:34.280 --> 00:23:35.915 align:middle line:84%
So, there's simple
heart focus techniques

00:23:35.915 --> 00:23:38.551 align:middle line:84%
to where you just
focus in your heart.

00:23:38.551 --> 00:23:41.654 align:middle line:84%
You bring your attention to
the physical area of the heart.

00:23:41.654 --> 00:23:45.525 align:middle line:84%
You learn just breath casually
in and out through that area,

00:23:45.525 --> 00:23:47.760 align:middle line:90%
but you take it a step further.

00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:51.330 align:middle line:84%
As you do that, you make an
effort then to just activate,

00:23:51.330 --> 00:23:53.833 align:middle line:84%
as best you can, a
positive emotion.

00:23:53.833 --> 00:23:57.503 align:middle line:84%
It may be hard when you're
upset and not easy to do.

00:23:57.503 --> 00:24:00.339 align:middle line:84%
A lot of times you can slow
down sort of the vibratory rate

00:24:00.339 --> 00:24:02.408 align:middle line:84%
