enough to start beginning

00:24:02.408 --> 00:24:05.611 align:middle line:84%
to maybe appreciate something
else, like I'm not happy

00:24:05.611 --> 00:24:11.017 align:middle line:84%
about this, but tomorrow,
I'm going to TLC.

00:24:11.017 --> 00:24:12.418 align:middle line:84%
