is a highly-ordered

00:27:27.680 --> 00:27:29.148 align:middle line:90%
and synchronized state,

00:27:29.148 --> 00:27:33.753 align:middle line:84%
where all the body's biological
systems begin to work together.

00:27:33.753 --> 00:27:36.322 align:middle line:84%
They all, what's happening
is they're all synchronizing

00:27:36.322 --> 00:27:38.290 align:middle line:84%
to the rhythmic beating
pattern of the heart,

00:27:38.290 --> 00:27:40.092 align:middle line:84%
which is the master and
the maker in our body.

00:27:40.092 --> 00:27:43.462 align:middle line:84%
So, digestion, respiration,
immune system response,

00:27:43.462 --> 00:27:46.799 align:middle line:84%
hormonal relations, all those
things begin to then synchronize

00:27:46.799 --> 00:27:51.470 align:middle line:84%
and line up with the rhythmic
beating pattern of the heart.

00:27:51.470 --> 00:27:55.808 align:middle line:84%
There's a psychological part
of it, because when you're

00:27:55.808 --> 00:27:56.942 align:middle line:90%
in the coherent state,

00:27:56.942 --> 00:27:59.945 align:middle line:84%
you naturally feel
more positive emotions.

00:27:59.945 --> 00:28:02.381 align:middle line:84%
You get to that state by
making an effort to feel them,

00:28:02.381 --> 00:28:03.949 align:middle line:84%
but once you're there,
they sort of flow,

00:28:03.949 --> 00:28:07.052 align:middle line:84%
and those positive emotions are
the ones we've already talked

00:28:07.052 --> 00:28:09.755 align:middle line:84%
