00:28:13.325 --> 00:28:15.327 align:middle line:90%
So, in the coherent state,

00:28:15.327 --> 00:28:17.763 align:middle line:84%
you have this highly-ordered
physiological

00:28:17.763 --> 00:28:20.499 align:middle line:84%
