societally collectively,

00:35:51.883 --> 00:35:56.922 align:middle line:84%
everything from hospital
admissions to health issues

00:35:56.922 --> 00:36:02.628 align:middle line:84%
to changes in the stock
market to the acceleration

00:36:02.628 --> 00:36:05.230 align:middle line:84%
