society like the Renaissance.

00:36:05.230 --> 00:36:06.665 align:middle line:84%
All of those things
have been tracked

00:36:06.665 --> 00:36:08.533 align:middle line:84%
to changes occurring
in these fields.

00:36:08.533 --> 00:36:10.836 align:middle line:84%
So, it's well-known
now and well-documented

00:36:10.836 --> 00:36:14.072 align:middle line:90%
