00:36:19.945 --> 00:36:23.148 align:middle line:84%
that mass human consciousness
is impacting those fields,

00:36:23.148 --> 00:36:27.886 align:middle line:84%
that we are all radiating
electromagnetically,

00:36:27.886 --> 00:36:29.254 align:middle line:90%
something from our hearts,

00:36:29.254 --> 00:36:31.723 align:middle line:84%
